---
import BaseLayout from "@layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---
<BaseLayout title="Cookie Policy" description="Cookie policy for guymi.github.io.">
  <div class="wrap-narrow" style="margin-top:3rem;">
    <h1>Cookie Policy</h1>
    <p><strong>Last updated:</strong> April 2026</p>
    <h2>What cookies we use</h2>
    <p>This site uses minimal cookies:</p>
    <ul>
      <li><strong>Essential:</strong> A consent cookie (<code>guymi-consent</code>) to remember your cookie preference. This cannot be disabled.</li>
      <li><strong>Analytics:</strong> Google Analytics 4 (enabled after you Accept via the consent banner).</li>
      <li><strong>Marketing:</strong> We do not use advertising or marketing cookies.</li>
    </ul>
    <h2>Third-party embeds</h2>
    <p>Some posts embed YouTube videos via <code>lite-youtube-embed</code>, which may set cookies only when you click play. No cookies are set by the embed before interaction.</p>
    <h2>Your choices</h2>
    <p>You can Accept or Reject non-essential cookies using the banner at the bottom of the site. You can reset your preference by clearing <code>guymi-consent</code> from localStorage.</p>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
